Many saw it even then because of its blatancy, but most weren't looking at the corrupt regime and seeing it for what it was. The way they viewed the country was totally different, so for a normie, there existed the ability for the lie to occupy some realm of plausible deniability in their mind. My parents went from seeing something was fishy but still thinking the news would cover it if there was an election fraud, to where now their immediate reaction was that Trump's failed assassination was the government trying to take out their political rival.

This year, the way the average person is looking at the country and the government is in a way that is 180 degrees different than they used to. All eyes are on the powers that be and Trump is even more popular. I'm even seeing people saying they were on the left but they're voting Trump now.

And the swing people can't be swayed so easily by the democrat lies. They look at their grocery bills, they look at the attempted coverup of Biden's mental degradation. It's a completely different world now, a world where X has much freedom of speech and people are allowed information that would have been suppressed in 2020. Not only is it allowed, often it's Elon Musk tweeting it out.

All eyes are on the political stage unlike ever before. You know how we, on the right were watching the corruption of the election like a hawk. Well now multiply that amount of people keeping their eyes peeled by many factors and you have the situation of 2024. Democrats are not in an enviable position.

Make them work hard for it, because the harder they have to work, the more mistakes that get made as they're rushing. You not voting just allows some election stealer a little less work for their job. Congrats, you just eased off the tension they're feeling rushing around trying to make things look feasible. Make them work for their evil, don't do their job for them and hand it to them on a silver platter.

No, that could be step 8 on a 10 or 20 step process that leads to people waking up and taking this country back. Vote whether they pull off the steal or not.
